265
00:13:00,746 --> 00:13:02,715
Wail till you see this place.

266
00:13:02,715 --> 00:13:04,717
Nobody's gonna bother us up there.

267
00:13:04,717 --> 00:13:06,552
And it's equal distance to the train station

268
00:13:06,552 --> 00:13:08,621
