269
00:13:08,621 --> 00:13:10,956
- [Mike] Better have a jacuzzi for 400 bucks.

270
00:13:10,956 --> 00:13:12,858
Mike this is it.

271
00:13:13,926 --> 00:13:15,928
Look, if the deal goes belly up,

272
00:13:15,928 --> 00:13:18,130
at least we'll be going out in style, right?

